ttps://mihaaru.com/news/68816 |url-status=live|archivedate=10 January 2021 |accessdate=10 January 2021 |df=dmy-all}}</ref> |- |2021 ! scope="row"|''Loabi Vevijje'' |Maajidh | | style="text-align:center;"|<ref>{{cite news|url=https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/67368 |title=End of filming for Loabi Vevijje |work=Mihaaru |last=Adhushan |first=Ahmed |date=10 April 2020 |archiveurl=http://archive.vn/wip/3V78T |url-status=live|archivedate=20 August 2020 |accessdate=20 August 2020 |df=dmy-all}}</ref> |- |2021 ! scope="row"|''Dheythee Aniyaa'' | | | |- |2021 ! scope="row"|''Lasviyas'' |Iqbal | | |- |}
